                    "id": "top_is_top_dead_dh_dT_ignored",
                    "description": "is_top = 0.0: the dh_dT multiplier is 0, so even a huge dh_dT = 1e6 must not affect T_np1. With H_i = 100 W/m², w_ice_n = w_liq_n = 0 (dry layer): H_residual = 100, T_np1 = 273.15 + 0.018*100 / (1 - 0*0.018*1e6) = 273.15 + 1.8 = 274.95 K. Confirms the is_top=0 masking is exact.",
