                            "type": "line",
                            "description": "T_np1 vs H_i for interior (is_top=0) and top (is_top=1, dh_dT=-10) variants on a dry layer. Both are linear; top variant has shallower slope by factor 1/1.18.",
                            "x": { "variable": "H_i", "label": "H_i (W/m²)" },
                            "y": { "variable": "T_np1", "label": "T_np1 (K)" }
